      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be verified under a documented SQA plan with version control, regression testing, and documented release notes at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "The commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) operates under a documented SQA plan meeting FDA guidance on software validation. Version control, regression test suites, and release documentation are available and were reviewed. Gradation 2 requirements satisfied."
    },
