      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification activities must demonstrate solver correctness for the governing equations relevant to blood pump hemolysis CFD at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) verification was performed for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver and the scalar hemolysis damage accumulation transport equation. Observed order of accuracy matched theoretical order for all test cases. Gradation 2 satisfied."
