    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device. The primary validation result demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy for worst-case hemolysis identification within the CPB operating envelope. The literature synthesis result provides the parameter foundation for the hemolysis model coefficient selection. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision that the CFD model can identify worst-case operating conditions for hemolysis with medium assurance.",
